1
00:00:40,399 --> 00:00:41,240
Help!

2
00:00:46,079 --> 00:00:47,679
I never should have

3
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:50,320
trusted that bitch.

4
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:51,640
Dad!

5
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:53,679
Zhu Yihai!

6
00:00:54,679 --> 00:00:56,079
I really wish I could live my life over.

7
00:00:57,079 --> 00:00:59,240
I want to live my life over too.

8
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:02,320
Help! Somebody help!

9
00:01:03,039 --> 00:01:03,840
Bro Hai!

10
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:05,200
What's wrong with you?

11
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,560
Save who?

12
00:01:07,079 --> 00:01:08,359
Save Zhu Yihai!

13
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:10,799
Bro, you are Zhu Yihai.

14
00:01:10,799 --> 00:01:12,000
I'm Zhu Yihai?

15
00:01:12,239 --> 00:01:13,040
Yeah.

16
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:14,879
Boss Lady, what's wrong with him?

17
00:01:14,879 --> 00:01:16,480
Don't tell me he's lost his memory.

18
00:01:30,519 --> 00:01:32,159
What year is it?

19
00:01:33,159 --> 00:01:34,799
1997.

20
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:37,120
I time-traveled.

21
00:01:37,879 --> 00:01:38,519
Dahai.

22
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:39,640
Anyway, you're awake now.

23
00:01:40,079 --> 00:01:40,920
Let's go home.

24
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,959
Go back? Go back where?

25
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,519
Back to the pool hall.

26
00:01:44,519 --> 00:01:45,560
Pool hall?

27
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:46,920
I really did become Zhu Yihai.

28
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:47,560
Zhu Yihai!

29
00:01:49,719 --> 00:01:50,480
Boss Lady!

30
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:53,719
You're not dead yet!

31
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,040
Another Boss Lady?

32
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:57,159
Hey, Dali, what are you yelling about?

33
00:01:58,359 --> 00:02:00,400
Qian Huilian, what are you doing here again?

34
00:02:00,519 --> 00:02:01,400
What?

35
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:04,159
Do I need to report to you to see Dahai?

36
00:02:06,159 --> 00:02:08,280
This old man has two girlfriends?

37
00:02:18,919 --> 00:02:20,120
Boss Lady, Boss Lady, Boss Lady!

38
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,319
I love eating bananas.

39
00:02:21,319 --> 00:02:22,680
I love eating bananas.

40
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:27,000
Who did I ever piss off?

41
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:28,520
Since you two already broke up,

42
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,879
stay away from Dahai from now on.

43
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,120
Dahai.

44
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,879
Don't forget our promise.

45
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,280
Dahai!

46
00:02:46,639 --> 00:02:48,360
What promise do you two have?

47
00:02:48,599 --> 00:02:50,759
We don't have any promises.

48
00:02:51,319 --> 00:02:52,120
I just...

49
00:02:54,479 --> 00:02:55,840
What the heck is vibrating?

50
00:03:00,439 --> 00:03:01,280
What is this?

51
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:02,680
It's a cell phone, obviously.

52
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,479
A cell phone?

53
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:04,800
This cell phone...

54
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:06,960
Brother Yihai!

55
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,280
Brother Yihai!

56
00:03:10,159 --> 00:03:10,960
Brother Yihai!

57
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,240
Are you alright?

58
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,319
Boss Long, you're here.

59
00:03:16,159 --> 00:03:18,000
Thanks to Brother Yihai stepping in,

60
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,560
otherwise I, Long Xiao,

61
00:03:20,039 --> 00:03:21,120
might've lost my life.

62
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:24,120
I'm not the type to forget a favor.

63
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,639
From now on, Brother Yihai

64
00:03:25,719 --> 00:03:27,400
is Giant Wood Group's Second-in-command.

65
00:03:27,639 --> 00:03:29,280
Greetings, Second-in-command!

66
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,919
Brother Yihai,

67
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:35,560
here, you're second to one,

68
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,639
above all others.

69
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:38,000
My Giant Wood Group

70
00:03:38,199 --> 00:03:40,080
will always be half yours, Brother Yihai.

71
00:03:40,319 --> 00:03:41,960
He has that kind of status too?

72
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:42,919
Let's go, brother.

73
00:03:43,639 --> 00:03:44,840
Big bro's throwing you a welcome dinner.

74
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:53,800
I actually time-traveled back to 1997,

75
00:03:54,319 --> 00:03:55,840
back when my dad was young.

76
00:03:56,719 --> 00:03:59,599
Today is November 10th, 1997.

77
00:03:59,599 --> 00:04:01,759
Now for today's midday news.

78
00:04:01,759 --> 00:04:04,280
Capital cultural figures held a forum on

79
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:07,439
the spirit of the 15th National Congress

80
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:08,080
to foster and flourish our culture.

81
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:10,759
November 1997.

82
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,520
Damn.

83
00:04:13,199 --> 00:04:15,639
The old man was jailed on Jan 1, 1998.

84
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:18,160
That's only a month or so away!

85
00:04:23,879 --> 00:04:25,560
This must be a dream.

86
00:04:31,639 --> 00:04:32,480
Brother Yihai.

87
00:04:33,199 --> 00:04:34,639
Get up and party with us!

88
00:04:36,759 --> 00:04:37,959
I can't go to prison.

89
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,399
Bro Hai, what are you talking about?

90
00:04:40,959 --> 00:04:41,839
Quick, knock on wood!

91
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,040
With me, Long Xiao, around,

92
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,639
how could I ever let you go to prison?

93
00:04:45,079 --> 00:04:45,879
Right?

94
00:04:45,879 --> 00:04:47,839
Right, with Boss Long looking out for us,

95
00:04:47,839 --> 00:04:49,000
there's no way you're going to prison.

96
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,160
Here, Boss Long,

97
00:04:50,519 --> 00:04:52,040
let me toast you on Bro Hai's behalf.

98
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:54,680
Who exactly sent the old man to prison?

99
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:57,639
Brother Yihai, join in!

100
00:04:58,079 --> 00:04:58,480
Come on!

101
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,600
Come on, today's such a happy day!

102
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,439
Bottoms up!

103
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:07,959
Hold on.

104
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,079
Come on, come on.

105
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:11,120
Hey, cut the music for a sec.

106
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,839
Everyone, gather around.

107
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,920
Come on, Brother Yihai,

108
00:05:16,079 --> 00:05:16,600
get over here.

109
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:17,920
Go on!

110
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,000
Hurry up, get over here.

111
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,560
Today,

112
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:26,399
I'm handing over all of Aimin Street

113
00:05:26,639 --> 00:05:27,439
to my brother.

114
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:28,319
Yes!

115
00:05:29,319 --> 00:05:30,360
All right, music back on.

116
00:05:30,879 --> 00:05:32,000
Let's keep drinking.

117
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:33,839
I object.

118
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,000
Xie Fan.

119
00:05:38,439 --> 00:05:39,279
What are you doing here?

120
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:42,800
Xie Fan.

121
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:45,319
Putting on a show?

122
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,600
I remember now.

123
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,439
The day my dad got out of prison,

124
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,959
he's the one who kidnapped me and my dad.

125
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,199
Xie Fan.

126
00:05:59,199 --> 00:06:00,399
You pulled a knife in the Night City fight.

127
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:01,639
You broke the rules.

128
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:02,439
Rules?

129
00:06:03,439 --> 00:06:05,759
You made me hide out for over 20 years,

130
00:06:05,759 --> 00:06:07,920
and now you're lecturing me about rules?

131
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:08,560
Don't you want to know

132
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:10,560
how your son has lived all these years?

133
00:06:11,319 --> 00:06:13,279
Come on, take a look.

134
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:17,240
He's a dog at my Foot Massage Parlor now.

135
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:21,279
You don't deserve to be my father.

136
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,040
Putting on a show?

137
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,000
Chaoyang.

138
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:54,800
Bro.

139
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,720
Didn't you promise Aimin Street to me?

140
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:00,600
Dongxing Factory just got demolished.

141
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:02,160
You won't just use and discard me, right?

142
00:07:02,399 --> 00:07:03,319
Listen, Xie Fan,

143
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,879
aren't you being a bit too hasty?

144
00:07:04,879 --> 00:07:06,120
Of course I'm hasty.

145
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,439
Because that belongs to me.

146
00:07:07,439 --> 00:07:09,160
Now you're giving it to this scumbag.

147
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,560
How can I not be hasty?

148
00:07:11,279 --> 00:07:12,839
So what if you're hasty? What can you do?

149
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,639
Today is Bro Hai's Victory Banquet.

150
00:07:17,079 --> 00:07:18,639
What you're doing makes it

151
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,399
really tough for Bro Hai.

152
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:25,240
Tough, huh?

153
00:07:28,319 --> 00:07:30,040
If it's tough, then forget it.

154
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,079
Xie Fan,

155
00:07:36,959 --> 00:07:38,120
you've gone too far.

156
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,399
And you, what are you tagging along for?

157
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:41,600
Starting a rebellion?

158
00:07:51,439 --> 00:07:52,959
Don't celebrate too soon.

159
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:58,759
Come on, Brother Yihai.

160
00:07:58,759 --> 00:07:59,959
Old hatreds and new grudges.

161
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,399
Hurry, don't mind them.

162
00:08:01,879 --> 00:08:02,639
These bastards.

163
00:08:02,639 --> 00:08:03,759
I'll discipline him when we get back.

164
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,319
Don't let it ruin our mood today.

165
00:08:05,519 --> 00:08:06,720
Come on, keep drinking.

166
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:07,800
Come on, keep singing.

167
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:08,800
Keep eating.

168
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,240
It's all on me, come on, keep going.

169
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,480
Let's keep going, keep going.

170
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:12,879
Come on, come on.

171
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:13,680
Come on.

172
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:17,000
Here, Boss Long.

173
00:08:21,839 --> 00:08:22,600
Drink up.

174
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,680
Bottoms up.

175
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:27,480
Zhu Yihai,

176
00:08:28,439 --> 00:08:30,199
you served 26 years in prison,

177
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,679
and I was an orphan for 26 years.

178
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:36,519
And now you're living it up.

179
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:39,159
I hate you,

180
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:40,600
Zhu Yihai.

181
00:09:03,879 --> 00:09:05,039
Zhu Yihai

182
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,039
So this is where you live?

183
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:09,320
I thought you were some big shot.

184
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:27,120
So this is what you look like.

185
00:09:28,879 --> 00:09:30,840
You really deserve a beating.

186
00:09:37,519 --> 00:09:39,080
How could I have become you?

187
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,480
How did I become you?

188
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:42,200
How did I end up as you?

189
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:47,240
What did I do to deserve this?

190
00:09:48,919 --> 00:09:50,840
The only sin I ever committed was...

191
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,960
having you as my father.

192
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:56,919
Do you know on New Year's Day, 1998,

193
00:09:56,919 --> 00:09:59,120
you got locked up for over twenty years?

194
00:09:59,679 --> 00:10:02,519
After you went to prison, my mom died.

195
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:05,279
I don't even know her name.

196
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,879
I grew up in an orphanage.

197
00:10:08,799 --> 00:10:10,240
Everyone who saw me

198
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:13,919
would kick me around.

199
00:10:13,919 --> 00:10:14,639
Kick me around.

200
00:10:15,879 --> 00:10:17,879
Your good friend Xie Fan

201
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,519
bullied me

202
00:10:19,519 --> 00:10:21,720
for over twenty years straight.

203
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:24,120
Do you know what twenty years feels like?

204
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,240
All because of you,

205
00:10:29,399 --> 00:10:32,200
I never felt any love growing up.

206
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:34,399
Because I had no love at all.

207
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:39,000
And now I've even become you.

208
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:42,279
I have to serve your twenty-year sentence.

209
00:10:42,279 --> 00:10:43,639
What am I doing this for?

210
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:57,840
You'll commit the crime in a month, right?

211
00:10:58,120 --> 00:11:00,559
If I don't commit the crime this month,

212
00:11:02,559 --> 00:11:04,720
I won't have to go to prison, right?

213
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,879
And maybe I can finally meet my mom?

214
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,240
Zhu Yihai,

215
00:11:20,399 --> 00:11:21,879
I'll show you

216
00:11:21,879 --> 00:11:24,519
what a real father looks like.
